&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.3810409&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;538&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/c5dgkgUuWRnow0qyMbao56xYdoaiapsVj8hnLFJeG7kXBCyk2a4sAY9kvEQQcFfX97Dh96sRUKlbtaBEIibic4AlA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;2.5&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;它是今年3月上线的全新智能录音笔C1，来自大家耳熟能详的品牌——搜狗。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;录音转文字准确率、翻译准确率都非常高，品质有保障，&lt;span&gt;专为采访、会议、学习、培训、翻译而生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5259259&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1080&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/c5dgkgUuWRnow0qyMbao56xYdoaiapsVjROibacB54t1dxmQIial3XLYdcg2uAyZplFibic47o6vhB2DwuicMH8jZg2w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section powered-by=&quot;xiumi.us&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;
